✅ 4) jQuery Effects

Q7 (🔥 MMI). What are jQuery effects?

jQuery effects are built-in methods to add animations like show/hide, fade, slide.

Must know:
$("#box").hide();
$("#box").show();
$("#box").toggle();

$("#box").fadeIn();
$("#box").fadeOut();
$("#box").fadeToggle();

$("#box").slideUp();
$("#box").slideDown();
$("#box").slideToggle();
