 ✅ 5) Basic AJAX with jQuery

⭐ What is AJAX?
✅ Answer (QC ready) : AJAX = Asynchronous JavaScript and XML
It allows sending/receiving data from server without reloading the page.

📌 Real use:
Login validation
Search suggestions
Load products dynamically

⭐ jQuery AJAX methods
1\) $.ajax() (most powerful)
2)$.get() (simple GET request)
3\) $.post() (simple POST request)

